{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"The future of life, where the unraveling of our biology --"},{"time":4000,"text":"and bring up the lights a little bit. I don't have any slides."},{"time":6000,"text":"I'm just going to talk --"},{"time":9000,"text":"about where that's likely to carry us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":11000,"text":"And you know, I saw all the visions"},{"time":15000,"text":"of the first couple of sessions."},{"time":17000,"text":"It almost made me feel a little bit guilty about having an uplifting talk"},{"time":20000,"text":"about the future."},{"time":22000,"text":"It felt wrong to do that in some way."},{"time":24000,"text":"And yet, I don't really think it is"},{"time":26000,"text":"because when it comes down to it,"},{"time":28000,"text":"it's this larger trajectory that is really what is going to remain --"},{"time":32000,"text":"what people in the future are going to remember about this period."}]},{"cues":[{"time":36000,"text":"I want to talk to you a little bit about"},{"time":39000,"text":"why the visions of Jeremy Rivkins,"},{"time":43000,"text":"who would like to ban these sorts of technologies,"},{"time":46000,"text":"or of the Bill Joys who would like to relinquish them,"},{"time":50000,"text":"are actually -- to follow those paths would be such a tragedy for us."},{"time":55000,"text":"I'm focusing on biology,"},{"time":58000,"text":"the biological sciences."},{"time":60000,"text":"The reason I'm doing that is because those are going to be"},{"time":63000,"text":"the areas that are the most significant to us."},{"time":67000,"text":"The reason for that is really very simple."},{"time":69000,"text":"It's because we're flesh and blood."},{"time":71000,"text":"We're biological creatures."},{"time":73000,"text":"And what we can do with our biology"},{"time":77000,"text":"is going to shape our future"},{"time":79000,"text":"and that of our children and that of their children --"},{"time":82000,"text":"whether we gain control over aging,"},{"time":84000,"text":"whether we learn to protect ourselves from Alzheimer's,"},{"time":88000,"text":"and heart disease, and cancer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":90000,"text":"I think that Shakespeare really put it very nicely."},{"time":94000,"text":"And I'm actually going to use his words in the same order that he did."},{"time":97000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":99000,"text":"He said, \"And so from hour to hour"},{"time":102000,"text":"we ripe and ripe."},{"time":105000,"text":"And then from hour to hour we rot and rot."},{"time":107000,"text":"And thereby hangs a tale.\""},{"time":109000,"text":"Life is short, you know."},{"time":111000,"text":"And we need to think about planning a little bit."},{"time":113000,"text":"We're all going to eventually, even in the developed world,"},{"time":118000,"text":"going to have to lose everything that we love."},{"time":121000,"text":"When you're beginning to rot a little bit,"},{"time":124000,"text":"all of the videos crammed into your head,"},{"time":126000,"text":"all of the extensions that extend your various powers,"},{"time":130000,"text":"are going to being to seem a little secondary."},{"time":134000,"text":"And you know, I'm getting a little bit gray -- so is Ray Kurzweil,"},{"time":138000,"text":"so is Eric Drexler."}]},{"cues":[{"time":140000,"text":"This is where it's really central to our lives."},{"time":143000,"text":"Now I know there's been a whole lot of hype"},{"time":145000,"text":"about our power to control biology."},{"time":148000,"text":"You just have to look at the Human Genome Project."},{"time":150000,"text":"It wasn't two years ago"},{"time":152000,"text":"that everybody was talking about --"},{"time":154000,"text":"we've found the Holy Grail of biology."},{"time":156000,"text":"We're deciphering the code of codes."},{"time":158000,"text":"We're reading the book of life."},{"time":161000,"text":"It's a little bit reminiscent of 1969 when Neil Armstrong walked on the moon,"},{"time":165000,"text":"and everybody was about to race out toward the stars."},{"time":169000,"text":"And we've all seen \"2001: A Space Odyssey.\""},{"time":172000,"text":"You know it's 2003, and there is no HAL."},{"time":176000,"text":"And there is no odyssey to our own moon, much less the moons of Jupiter."},{"time":180000,"text":"And we're still picking up pieces of the Challenger."},{"time":183000,"text":"So it's not surprising that some people would wonder"},{"time":187000,"text":"whether maybe 30 or 40 years from now,"},{"time":190000,"text":"we'll look back at this instant in time,"},{"time":192000,"text":"and all of the sort of talk about"},{"time":195000,"text":"the Human Genome Project,"},{"time":197000,"text":"and what all this is going to mean to us --"},{"time":199000,"text":"well, it will really mean precious little."},{"time":203000,"text":"And I just want to say that that is absolutely not going to be the case."},{"time":207000,"text":"Because when we talk about our genetics and our biology,"},{"time":212000,"text":"and modifying and altering and adjusting these things,"},{"time":214000,"text":"we're talking about changing ourselves."},{"time":217000,"text":"And this is very critical stuff."}]},{"cues":[{"time":219000,"text":"If you have any doubts about how technology affects our lives,"},{"time":223000,"text":"you just have to go to any major city."},{"time":225000,"text":"This is not the stomping ground"},{"time":227000,"text":"of our Pleistocene ancestors."},{"time":229000,"text":"What's happening is we're taking this technology --"},{"time":232000,"text":"it's becoming more precise, more potent --"},{"time":234000,"text":"and we're turning it back upon ourselves."},{"time":237000,"text":"Before it's all done"},{"time":239000,"text":"we are going to alter ourselves"},{"time":241000,"text":"every bit as much as we have changed the world around us."},{"time":244000,"text":"It's going to happen a lot sooner"},{"time":246000,"text":"than people imagine."},{"time":248000,"text":"On the way there it's going to"},{"time":251000,"text":"completely revolutionize medicine and health care; that's obvious."},{"time":254000,"text":"It's going to change the way we have children."},{"time":256000,"text":"It's going to change the way we manage"},{"time":258000,"text":"and alter our emotions."},{"time":260000,"text":"It's going to probably change the human lifespan."},{"time":262000,"text":"It will really make us question"},{"time":264000,"text":"what it is to be a human being."}]},{"cues":[{"time":268000,"text":"The larger context of this is that are"},{"time":270000,"text":"two unprecedented revolutions that are going on today."},{"time":276000,"text":"The first of them is the obvious one,"},{"time":278000,"text":"the silicon revolution,"},{"time":280000,"text":"which you all are very, very familiar with."},{"time":283000,"text":"It's changing our lives in so many ways,"},{"time":285000,"text":"and it will continue to do that."},{"time":287000,"text":"What the essence of that is, is that we're taking"},{"time":289000,"text":"the sand at our feet, the inert silicon at our feet,"},{"time":293000,"text":"and we're breathing a level of complexity into it"},{"time":295000,"text":"that rivals that of life itself,"},{"time":297000,"text":"and may even surpass it."},{"time":300000,"text":"As an outgrowth of that, as a child of that revolution,"},{"time":303000,"text":"is the revolution in biology."}]},{"cues":[{"time":305000,"text":"The genomics revolution,"},{"time":307000,"text":"proteomics, metabolomics, all of these \"omics\""},{"time":310000,"text":"that sound so terrific on grants and on business plans."},{"time":313000,"text":"What we're doing is we are"},{"time":318000,"text":"seizing control of our evolutionary future."},{"time":321000,"text":"I mean we're essentially using technology"},{"time":323000,"text":"to just jam evolution into fast-forward."},{"time":326000,"text":"It's not at all clear where it's going to take us."},{"time":329000,"text":"But in five to ten years we're going to start see"},{"time":332000,"text":"some very profound changes."},{"time":334000,"text":"The most immediate changes that we'll see"},{"time":336000,"text":"are things like in medicine."},{"time":338000,"text":"There is going to be a big shift towards preventative medicine"},{"time":341000,"text":"as we start to be able to identify"},{"time":343000,"text":"all of the risk factors that we have as individuals."},{"time":346000,"text":"But who is going to pay for all this?"},{"time":348000,"text":"And how are we going to understand all this complex information?"},{"time":352000,"text":"That is going to be the IT challenge"},{"time":355000,"text":"of the next generation, is communicating all this information."}]},{"cues":[{"time":359000,"text":"There's pharmacogenomics, the combination of pharmacology"},{"time":361000,"text":"and genetics:"},{"time":364000,"text":"tailoring drugs to our individual constitutions"},{"time":366000,"text":"that Juan talked about a little bit earlier."},{"time":369000,"text":"That's going to have amazing impacts."},{"time":372000,"text":"And it's going to be used for diet as well,"},{"time":375000,"text":"and nutritional supplements and such."},{"time":377000,"text":"But it's going to have a big impact because"},{"time":379000,"text":"we're going to have niche drugs."},{"time":381000,"text":"And we aren't going to be able to support"},{"time":384000,"text":"the kinds of expenses that we have to create blockbuster drugs today."},{"time":387000,"text":"The approval process is going to fall apart, actually."},{"time":392000,"text":"It's too slow."},{"time":394000,"text":"It's too risk-averse."},{"time":396000,"text":"And it is really not suited for the future"},{"time":399000,"text":"that we're moving into."}]},{"cues":[{"time":401000,"text":"Another thing is that we're just going to have to deal with this knowledge."},{"time":403000,"text":"It's really wonderful when we hear,"},{"time":405000,"text":"\"Oh, 99.9 percent of the letters in the code are the same."},{"time":410000,"text":"We're all identical to each other. Isn't it wonderful?\""},{"time":414000,"text":"And look around you and know"},{"time":416000,"text":"that what we really care about is"},{"time":418000,"text":"that little bit of difference."},{"time":420000,"text":"We look the same to a visitor from another planet, maybe,"},{"time":423000,"text":"but not to each other"},{"time":425000,"text":"because we compete with each other all time."},{"time":427000,"text":"And we're going to have to come to grips with the fact"},{"time":430000,"text":"that there are differences between us as individuals that we will know about,"},{"time":433000,"text":"and between subpopulations of humans as well."},{"time":437000,"text":"To deny that that's the case is not a very good start on that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":441000,"text":"A generation or so away"},{"time":444000,"text":"there are going to be even more profound things that are going to happen."},{"time":447000,"text":"That's when we're going to begin to use this knowledge to modify ourselves."},{"time":451000,"text":"Now I don't mean extra gills or something --"},{"time":454000,"text":"something we care about, like aging."},{"time":456000,"text":"What if we could unravel aging and understand it --"},{"time":460000,"text":"begin to retard the process or even reverse it?"},{"time":463000,"text":"It would change absolutely everything."},{"time":465000,"text":"And it's obvious to anyone,"},{"time":467000,"text":"that if we can do this, we absolutely will do this,"},{"time":470000,"text":"whatever the consequences are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":472000,"text":"The second is modifying our emotions."},{"time":476000,"text":"I mean Ritalin, Viagra,"},{"time":480000,"text":"things of that sort, Prozac."},{"time":482000,"text":"You know, this is just clumsy little baby steps."},{"time":484000,"text":"What if you could take a little"},{"time":487000,"text":"concoction of pharmaceuticals"},{"time":490000,"text":"that would make you feel really contented,"},{"time":493000,"text":"just happy to be you."},{"time":495000,"text":"Are you going to be able to resist that if it doesn't have any overt side effects?"},{"time":498000,"text":"Probably not."},{"time":500000,"text":"And if you don't, who are you going to be?"},{"time":502000,"text":"Why do you do what you do?"},{"time":504000,"text":"We're sort of circumventing evolutionary programs that guide our behavior."},{"time":507000,"text":"It's going to be very challenging to deal with."}]},{"cues":[{"time":509000,"text":"The third area is reproduction."},{"time":513000,"text":"The idea that we're going to chose our children's genes,"},{"time":516000,"text":"as we begin to understand what genes say about who we are."},{"time":520000,"text":"That's the focus of my book \"Redesigning Humans,\""},{"time":522000,"text":"where I talk about the kinds of choices we'll make,"},{"time":524000,"text":"and the challenges it's going to present to society."},{"time":527000,"text":"There are three obvious ways of doing this."},{"time":529000,"text":"The first is cloning."},{"time":531000,"text":"It didn't happen."},{"time":533000,"text":"It's a total media circus."},{"time":535000,"text":"It will happen in five to 10 years."},{"time":537000,"text":"And when it does it's not going to be that big a deal."},{"time":540000,"text":"The birth of a delayed identical twin"},{"time":542000,"text":"is not going to shake western civilization."}]},{"cues":[{"time":547000,"text":"But there are more important things that are already occurring:"},{"time":550000,"text":"embryo screening."},{"time":552000,"text":"You take a six to eight cell embryo,"},{"time":555000,"text":"you tease out one of the cells, you run a genetic test on that cell,"},{"time":558000,"text":"and depending on the results of that test"},{"time":560000,"text":"you either implant that embryo or you discard it."},{"time":563000,"text":"It's already done to avoid rare diseases today."},{"time":566000,"text":"And pretty soon it's going to be possible"},{"time":569000,"text":"to avoid virtually all genetic diseases in that way."},{"time":573000,"text":"As that becomes possible"},{"time":576000,"text":"this is going to move from something that is used by those who"},{"time":579000,"text":"have infertility problems and are already doing in vitro fertilization,"},{"time":582000,"text":"to the wealthy who want to protect their children,"},{"time":585000,"text":"to just about everybody else."},{"time":587000,"text":"And in that process that's going to morph"},{"time":589000,"text":"from being just for diseases,"},{"time":591000,"text":"to being for lesser vulnerabilities,"},{"time":593000,"text":"like risk of manic depression or something,"},{"time":596000,"text":"to picking personalities,"},{"time":599000,"text":"temperaments, traits, these sorts of things."},{"time":602000,"text":"Of course there is going to be genetic engineering."},{"time":605000,"text":"Directly going in -- it's a little bit further away, but not that far away --"},{"time":608000,"text":"going in and altering the genes in the first cell in an embryo."},{"time":613000,"text":"The way I suspect it will happen"},{"time":616000,"text":"is using artificial chromosomes"},{"time":618000,"text":"and extra chromosomes, so we go from 46"},{"time":621000,"text":"to 47 or 48."},{"time":623000,"text":"And one that is not heritable"},{"time":625000,"text":"because who would want to pass on to their children"},{"time":628000,"text":"the archaic enhancement modules"},{"time":631000,"text":"that they got 25 years earlier from their parents?"},{"time":634000,"text":"It's a joke; of course they wouldn't want to do that."},{"time":637000,"text":"They'll want the new release."}]},{"cues":[{"time":639000,"text":"Those kinds of loose analogies with"},{"time":642000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":643000,"text":"computers, and with programming,"},{"time":645000,"text":"are actually much deeper than that."},{"time":648000,"text":"They are really going to come to operate in this realm."},{"time":651000,"text":"Now not everything that can be done should be done."},{"time":654000,"text":"And it won't be done."},{"time":656000,"text":"But when something is feasible in thousands of"},{"time":658000,"text":"laboratories all over the world,"},{"time":660000,"text":"which is going to be the case with these technologies,"},{"time":662000,"text":"when there are large numbers of people who see them as beneficial,"},{"time":664000,"text":"which is already the case,"},{"time":666000,"text":"and when they're almost impossible to police,"},{"time":669000,"text":"it's not a question of if this is going to happen,"},{"time":671000,"text":"it's when and where and how it's going to happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":673000,"text":"Humanity is going to go down this path."},{"time":677000,"text":"And it's going to do so for two reasons."},{"time":679000,"text":"The first is that all these technologies"},{"time":682000,"text":"are just a spin-off of mainstream medical research"},{"time":684000,"text":"that everybody wants to see happen."},{"time":686000,"text":"It is being funded very very --"},{"time":689000,"text":"in a big way."},{"time":691000,"text":"The second is, we're human."},{"time":693000,"text":"That's what we do."},{"time":695000,"text":"We try and use our technology to"},{"time":697000,"text":"improve our lives in one way or another."},{"time":699000,"text":"To imagine that we're not going to use these technologies"},{"time":702000,"text":"when they become available,"},{"time":704000,"text":"is as much a denial of who we are"},{"time":706000,"text":"as to imagine"},{"time":708000,"text":"that we'll use these technologies and not fret"},{"time":710000,"text":"and worry about it a great deal."},{"time":713000,"text":"The lines are going to blur. And they already are"},{"time":716000,"text":"between therapy and enhancement,"},{"time":718000,"text":"between treatment and prevention,"},{"time":720000,"text":"between need and desire."},{"time":723000,"text":"That's really the central one, I believe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":726000,"text":"People can try and ban these things."},{"time":728000,"text":"They undoubtedly will. They have."},{"time":730000,"text":"But ultimately all this is going to do"},{"time":732000,"text":"is just shift development elsewhere."},{"time":735000,"text":"It's going to drive these things from view."},{"time":737000,"text":"It's going to reserve the technology for the wealthy"},{"time":739000,"text":"because they are in the best position"},{"time":741000,"text":"to circumvent any of these sorts of laws."},{"time":744000,"text":"And it's going to deny us"},{"time":746000,"text":"the information that we need to make wise decisions"},{"time":748000,"text":"about how to use these technologies."},{"time":751000,"text":"So, sure, we need to debate these things."},{"time":753000,"text":"And I think it's wonderful that we do."},{"time":755000,"text":"But we shouldn't kid ourselves"},{"time":758000,"text":"and think that we're going to reach a consensus about these things."},{"time":761000,"text":"That is simply not going to happen."},{"time":763000,"text":"They touch us too deeply."},{"time":765000,"text":"And they depend too much upon history, upon philosophy,"},{"time":768000,"text":"upon religion, upon culture, upon politics."},{"time":771000,"text":"Some people are going to see this"},{"time":774000,"text":"as an abomination,"},{"time":776000,"text":"as the worst thing, as just awful."},{"time":779000,"text":"Other people are going to say, \"This is great."},{"time":782000,"text":"This is the flowering of human endeavor.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":786000,"text":"The one thing though that is really dangerous"},{"time":789000,"text":"about these sorts of technologies,"},{"time":792000,"text":"is that it's easy to become seduced by them."},{"time":796000,"text":"And to focus too much on all"},{"time":798000,"text":"the high-technology possibilities that exist."},{"time":801000,"text":"And to lose touch"},{"time":804000,"text":"with the basic rhythms of our biology and our health."},{"time":806000,"text":"There are too many people that think that high-technology medicine"},{"time":809000,"text":"is going to keep them, save them,"},{"time":811000,"text":"from overeating,"},{"time":813000,"text":"from eating a lot of fast foods,"},{"time":815000,"text":"from not getting any exercise."},{"time":817000,"text":"It's not going to happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":819000,"text":"In the midst of all this amazing technology,"},{"time":821000,"text":"and all these things that are occurring, it's really interesting"},{"time":824000,"text":"because there is sort of a counter-revolution that is going on:"},{"time":827000,"text":"a resurgence of interest in remedies from the past,"},{"time":832000,"text":"in nutraceuticals, in all of these sorts of things"},{"time":835000,"text":"that some people, in the pharmaceutical industry particularly,"},{"time":838000,"text":"like to brand as non-science."},{"time":840000,"text":"But this whole effort is generated,"},{"time":843000,"text":"is driven, by IT as well"},{"time":846000,"text":"because that is how we're gathering all this information,"},{"time":849000,"text":"and linking it, and integrating it together."},{"time":851000,"text":"There is a lot in this rich biota that is going to serve us well."},{"time":856000,"text":"And that's where about half of our drugs come."},{"time":858000,"text":"So we shouldn't dismiss this"},{"time":860000,"text":"because it's an enormous opportunity to use"},{"time":862000,"text":"these sorts of results,"},{"time":865000,"text":"or these random loose trials from the last thousand years"},{"time":868000,"text":"about what has impacts on our health."},{"time":870000,"text":"And to use our advanced technologies"},{"time":872000,"text":"to pull out what is beneficial from this"},{"time":874000,"text":"sea of noise, basically."}]},{"cues":[{"time":877000,"text":"In fact this isn't just abstract."},{"time":880000,"text":"I just formed a biotechnology company"},{"time":882000,"text":"that is using"},{"time":884000,"text":"this sort of an approach to develop"},{"time":886000,"text":"therapeutics for Alzheimer's and other diseases of aging,"},{"time":889000,"text":"and we're making some real progress."},{"time":891000,"text":"So here we are."},{"time":893000,"text":"It's the beginning of a new millennium."},{"time":896000,"text":"If you look forward,"},{"time":898000,"text":"I mean future humans,"},{"time":900000,"text":"far before the end of this millennium,"},{"time":903000,"text":"in a few hundred years, they are going to look back at this moment."},{"time":905000,"text":"And from the beginning of today's sessions"},{"time":908000,"text":"you'd think that they're going to see this as this horrible"},{"time":911000,"text":"difficult, painful period"},{"time":913000,"text":"that we struggled through."},{"time":915000,"text":"And I don't think that's what's going to happen."},{"time":918000,"text":"They're going to do like everybody does. They are going to forget about all that stuff."},{"time":922000,"text":"And they are actually going to romanticize this moment in time."},{"time":925000,"text":"They are going to think about it"},{"time":927000,"text":"as this glorious instant"},{"time":929000,"text":"when we laid down"},{"time":931000,"text":"the very foundations of their lives,"},{"time":934000,"text":"of their society, of their future."},{"time":936000,"text":"You know it's a little bit like a birth."},{"time":940000,"text":"Where there is this bloody, awful mess happens."},{"time":943000,"text":"And then what comes out of it? New life."},{"time":947000,"text":"Actually as was pointed out earlier,"},{"time":950000,"text":"we forget about all the struggle there was in getting there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":953000,"text":"So to me,"},{"time":957000,"text":"it's clear that one of the foundations of that future"},{"time":959000,"text":"is going to be the reworking of our biology."},{"time":963000,"text":"It's going to come gradually at first. It's going to pick up speed."},{"time":965000,"text":"We're going to make lots of errors."},{"time":967000,"text":"That's the way these things work."},{"time":969000,"text":"To me it's an incredible privilege"},{"time":972000,"text":"to be alive now"},{"time":974000,"text":"and to be able to witness this thing."},{"time":977000,"text":"It is something that is a unique instant"},{"time":979000,"text":"in the history of all of life."},{"time":982000,"text":"It will always be remembered."},{"time":984000,"text":"And what's extraordinary is that"},{"time":986000,"text":"we're not just observing this,"},{"time":988000,"text":"we are the architects of this."},{"time":990000,"text":"I think that we should be proud of it."},{"time":992000,"text":"What is so difficult and challenging"},{"time":995000,"text":"is that we are also the objects of these changes."},{"time":998000,"text":"It's our health, it's our lives, it's our future, it's our children."},{"time":1001000,"text":"And that is why they are so very troubling to so many people"},{"time":1005000,"text":"who would pull back in fear."},{"time":1008000,"text":"I think that our choice"},{"time":1011000,"text":"in the choice of life,"},{"time":1013000,"text":"is not whether we're going to go down this path."},{"time":1016000,"text":"We are, definitely."},{"time":1018000,"text":"It's how we hold it in our hearts."},{"time":1021000,"text":"It's how we look at it."},{"time":1023000,"text":"I think Thucydides really spoke to us very clearly"},{"time":1026000,"text":"in 430 B.C. He put it nicely."},{"time":1030000,"text":"Again, I'll use the words in the same order he did."},{"time":1033000,"text":"\"The bravest are surely those"},{"time":1037000,"text":"who have the clearest vision of what is before them,"},{"time":1040000,"text":"both glory and danger alike."},{"time":1043000,"text":"And yet notwithstanding, they go out and they meet it.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1047000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":1049000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}